, and icu ventilator; and opthalmology products, including galilean and prismatic loupe, spot illuminator, surgical camera, ttl loupe, light source, slit lamp microscope, and operating microscope. In addition, the company offers surgical disposables, such as meditapes, intravenous infusion sets, and oximeters. Further, it provides a turnkey dialysis center, imaging and diagnostic center, modular intensive care unit, modular operation theater, oncology labs and treatment centers, blood bank, and dental clinic setup services. Hemant Surgical Industries Limited was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}